mputer is housed in a 5,600 square foot space, roughly the size of two tennis courts and weighs nearly as much as a commercial airplane." SOURCES: BBC, Quartzhttps://www.bbc.com/news/technology-44439515https://qz.com/1301510/the-us-has-the-worlds-fastest-supercomputer-again-the-200-petaflop-summit/***]]></description>
